<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.esquire.com/features/what-ive-learned/learned-andy-grove-0500">"What I've Learned: Andy Grove"</a>, <i>Esquire</i> magazine, May 1, 2000</span></li>
